        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.12+13</title>
            <!-- sparkle:version is for build number, where sparkle:shortVersionString is
            responsible for build name -->
            <sparkle:version>13</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.12</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h1>Release notes - 1.0.12+13</h1>

                <h2>Features:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added floating button at the statistics screen to export data table as a CSV file, while preserving format, amount of rows and columns and sorting order.</li>
                    <li>Added possibility to pause tracking activity for a set period of time.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Fixes:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed issue with "Work time" and "Desk time" not calculating correctly.</li>
                    <li>Fixed issue with statistics showing incorrect or no data at all.</li>
                    <li>Fixed multiple issues with applications not having correct names or not showing even with activity being present.</li>
                    <li>Fixed issue with productive time showing over 100% productivity.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wen, 14 Aug 2025 10:00:00</pubDate>
